            <li data-en="Has supported STAR program funding. Denver voters approved municipal broadband in 2020; the city has not built it under Johnston's administration." data-es="Ha apoyado el financiamiento del programa STAR. Los votantes de Denver aprobaron la banda ancha municipal en 2020; la ciudad no la ha construido bajo la administración de Johnston.">Has supported STAR program funding. Denver voters approved municipal broadband in 2020; <strong>the city has not built it</strong> under Johnston's administration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <details class="candidate-responses">
          <summary data-en="View Questionnaire Responses" data-es="Ver Respuestas del Cuestionario">View Questionnaire Responses</summary>
          <div class="responses-pending">
