          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Lisa Calderón -->
      <div class="candidate-card">
        <div class="candidate-header">
          <div class="candidate-info">
            <h3>Lisa Calder&oacute;n</h3>
            <span class="candidate-tag" data-en="Justice Advocate, Executive Director of Women Uprising" data-es="Defensora de Justicia, Directora Ejecutiva de Women Uprising">Justice Advocate, Executive Director of Women Uprising</span>
          </div>
          <span class="response-status response-status--pending" data-en="Questionnaire Sent" data-es="Cuestionario Enviado">Questionnaire Sent</span>
        </div>
        <div class="candidate-context">
          <h4 data-en="What We Know From the Public Record" data-es="Lo Que Sabemos del Registro Público">What We Know From the Public Record</h4>
          <ul>
            <li data-en="Third mayoral run. Finished third in 2023 with 18.21% of the vote — 3,200 votes and two points short of the runoff. Fourth-generation Denverite. Holds a bachelor's in English, master's in liberal studies, law degree, and doctorate in education." data-es="Tercera candidatura a la alcaldía. Terminó tercera en 2023 con el 18.21% de los votos — 3,200 votos y dos puntos por debajo de la segunda vuelta. Denverita de cuarta generación. Posee una licenciatura en inglés, maestría en estudios liberales, título de abogada y doctorado en educación.">Third mayoral run. Finished third in 2023 with 18.21% — 3,200 votes short of the runoff. Fourth-generation Denverite. Holds a <strong>bachelor's, master's, JD, and EdD</strong>.</li>
